{"type": "article", "id": 21897, "title": "玻璃花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-04T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115137AFHUX1iTtJObvx6Y.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">玻璃的艺术表现是常常被设计师开发，意大利设计师 elena salmistraro 带来了一组玻璃容器就发挥了玻璃的重叠效果。它的外形有点像一盏小灯，有带菱形纹路的圆锥形底座和灯笼似的灯罩，中间空出了一根细长的玻璃柱，从上至下，和透明与半透明的玻璃外壳重叠，形成了三种不同的效果，有层次感。它可以用来当做花瓶使用。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151331r6ASYmvFRyfJVxl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.14914425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115133m1lNAuE9g8HRGVXf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115134aIuZYU3qwMEo5jpz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115134hy0ZKXaeEjNcMnFk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}